OL,2,MAwe and Wonder in the Sky
OL,4,CLucy Rogers
OL,5,CFri 18:00-18:30
OL,6,CStage B
OL,8,GA story-driven talk about the hidden
OL,9,Gscience of light and the sky, told
OL,10,Gthrough encounters including searching
OL,11,Gfor glow worms and chasing comets. And
OL,12,Ga #RobotWars Easter egg. Starting in
OL,13,Gthe air around us, we travel upwards
OL,14,Ginto the sky and finally in to space.
OL,15,GBetween these two stories are the bits
OL,16,Gof science we often walk under without
OL,17,Gnoticing: why the sky changes colour,
OL,18,Gwhat darkness reveals, how light
OL,19,Gbehaves, and how small observations
OL,20,Gcan lead to much bigger questions.
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
